    "summary": "The user, playing the role of a debate coach, asks the assistant to help students develop sophisticated \"steelman\" arguments for a specific side of a controversial political debate (pro-border security). The assistant provides high-level arguments regarding sovereignty, national security, labor market integrity, and fiscal responsibility, and finally provides a strategy to counter human rights-based rebuttals by reframing the legal framework as a prerequisite for rights.",
